Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.60,Top,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,MF Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.74,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And the order is suddenly shuffled!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:23.63,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The spray from the intense rain is \Nmaking it hard to tell what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:29.05,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,With their superior traction, three 4x4 cars\Nseem to have won the dash away from the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:32.55,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Oishi in the 3 car\Novertakes Maezono in the 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.31,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And Sakamoto in the 5\N sails past Taylor in the 8 car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:40.98,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,At the back, Aiba in the 10 car \Npulls ahead of Kitahara in the 18!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:46.03,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,The handicap system in the regulations\N Ryo Takahashi came up with
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:50.82,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,is generally believed to be \Npretty harsh on 4x4 cars in the dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:54.55,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,But when moisture's involved, \Nthis level of traction becomes an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.91,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna establish a real lead this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.66,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Moments like this are \Nwhat 4x4 drive is meant for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.59,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\bord0\fnImpact\shad0\fsp16\fax-0.37\c&HB68D7A&\frz17.24\frx358\fry354\pos(388,158)}Ashinoko Skyline
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.59,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a change of position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.26,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Moe-chan, Mami-chan, \Nif you'd do the honors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:10.93,Default,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,What? Already? But they only just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.83,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold the umbrella for you \Nso you don't get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:16.39,Default,Mami,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.58,Default,Mami,0000,0000,0000,,My butt's not ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.56,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Beckenbauer leads the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:30.40,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And Sawatari in the 4 \Nis sticking to his bumper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:34.45,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The finish line awaits at the end \Nof three laps totaling 75.9km,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:38.58,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,with 15 drivers kicking up \Na fine mist in their wake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:44.42,Italics,Sawatari,0000,0000,0000,,I love the rain. All the power \Nin the world won't help you in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:48.42,Italics,Sawatari,0000,0000,0000,,It's like being forced to lay down your \Nweapons and duke it out with your fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.42,Italics,Sawatari,0000,0000,0000,,Who's really the fastest here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.43,Italics,Sawatari,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to clear that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.56,Italics,Beckenbauer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me lightly, Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.02,Italics,Beckenbauer,0000,0000,0000,,I have absolute confidence in \Nmy ability to deal with wet roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.90,Italics,Beckenbauer,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a single factor that will \Nmake me lose to a Japanese driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:22.12,Italics,Maezono,0000,0000,0000,,I might've lost out to that 4x4 Huracán\N in the dash away from the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.33,Italics,Maezono,0000,0000,0000,,but that won't matter \Nonce I've picked up enough speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.84,Italics,Maezono,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the Lambo in front of me, \Nand the Ferrari in front of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:32.72,Italics,Maezono,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a position to take on the \NItalian manufacturers that rule the roost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.55,Italics,Maezono,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show 'em \Nwhat a Honda is capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:41.38,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Another question for you, Ikeda-san:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:47.39,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,How do you suppose this rain will affect \Nthe road conditions in the death zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.50,Default,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,I expect it'll be horrendous there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.65,Default,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,The rain will prevent\N any new ash from building up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:58.80,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,but anything already on the road will turn \Ninto a free-flowing sludge so slippery,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.38,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,the drivers will be severely limited by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:08.08,Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say the death zone will require the \Nutmost caution, especially on this first lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:13.09,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The column of spray makes its way \Nthrough Ashinoko Skyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.89,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The leading group \Nplunges into the slip trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.49,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Battling understeer, \Nthe 3 car ends up going wide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:48.08,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The 13 moves ahead\N like it slid right past him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.99,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:54.42,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was being careful, \Nbut I still ended up sliding that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.30,Italics,Maezono,0000,0000,0000,,That was some pretty \Nsloppy steering, Oishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:01.93,Italics,Maezono,0000,0000,0000,,It just goes to show that four-wheel drive \Nis no help when going into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:35.64,Italics,Yanagida,0000,0000,0000,,He's not drifting like \Nhe was in qualifying, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:39.93,Italics,Yanagida,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he's pretty fast\Neven without doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.47,Italics,Yanagida,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a big bag of tricks \Nfor such a young guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:48.24,Italics,Yanagida,0000,0000,0000,,But me and my car are no slouches \Nwhen it comes to cornering, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:56.54,Italics,Yanagida,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you show me exactly\Nhow a "super rookie" races?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.62,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sliding all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.81,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so damn slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.42,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap, this is so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.29,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,I love this sorta thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:18.46,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,While their tires scrabble for grip\Non the death zone's asphalt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:24.17,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,the chosen 15 are proving their mettle\Nby fearlessly keeping their foot on the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:31.64,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The 12 and the 4 are extending their lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.92,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The 1 car can't stay with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:41.02,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The Godly Fifteen are stretching out and \Nbreaking up into a number of smaller groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:46.99,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Ikeda-san, has anything caught \Nyour attention about the race so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.82,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:55.17,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I'm paying close attention \Nto the 86 in the middle of the pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:20:00.76,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,It's the one car that didn't alter its \Ndriving style on entering the death zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:05.10,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,The way it is so steady \Nthrough this section is almost eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:10.73,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Kanata actually rallied his way \Nthrough the death zone in qualifying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:14.35,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,setting a new record for that sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:19.51,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, he's now demonstrating\N a completely different kind of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.18,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,That's just it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:25.32,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,The way he's driving seems to scream,\N "The race has only just begun,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.99,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,and I find that more than a bit unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.61,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,The leading group roars past\Nthe Kojiri Pass junction,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:38.99,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,and the course turns downhill from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:42.01,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,They can't afford a moment's\N carelessness from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:46.47,Top Italics,Ikeda,0000,0000,0000,,A single mistake can cost you your life\N when racing downhill in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.68,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,We invested a lot in this GTR,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.94,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,but all this rain is\N making it a handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:02.67,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,The traction control and \Nstability control keep butting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.21,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a 2-liter NA\N is pushing me this hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:12.37,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,But in these conditions, even someone \Nwho's good at zipping downhill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:16.50,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,can't fight physics \Nand take the corners any faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.62,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep my line tight \Ninto and around each corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:23.27,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,he'll be forced to sit \Nbehind me, feeling frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.64,Italics,Yanagida,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now. What the hell is he planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:33.56,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,Around the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.52,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.56,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:48.07,Italics,Otani,0000,0000,0000,,The roads are so wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.49,Italics,Yanagida,0000,0000,0000,,So how is he going so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.69,Italics,Yanagida/Otani,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:36.47,Italics,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Turn 15: \NThe Relay Straight Yin-Yang.